-- Honda U.S. March sales rise adjusted 4.2 percent
-- 
-- Tue Apr 1, 2008 1:38pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/01/us-honda-sales-idUSWNAS654120080401

 

 DETROIT  (Reuters) - Honda Motor Co Ltd ( 7267.T ) said on Tuesday that U.S. sales rose 4.2 percent in March to 138,734 vehicles on an adjusted basis that takes into account two fewer selling days compared with a year earlier. 

 Overall, Honda said it sold 83,214 cars, up from 80,633 a year earlier, while truck sales declined to 55,520 for the month, from 62,759 a year earlier. (Reporting by  David Bailey )